# vendor-connectors Development

## Package Overview

Universal vendor connectors including Meshy AI for 3D generation.

## Commands

```bash
uv sync --extra tests    # Install deps
uv run pytest tests/ -v  # Run tests
uvx ruff check src/      # Lint
uv build                 # Build package
```

## Connectors

- AWS, Google Cloud, GitHub, Slack, Vault, Zoom
- Meshy AI (3D asset generation)

## Key Patterns

- Python 3.10+ (crewai requirement)
- Use absolute imports
- Meshy module at `vendor_connectors.meshy`
